      • getGraphData

        java.util.List<java.lang.String[]> getGraphData()
        Returns a List<String[]> object containing the parsed input graph data. Each String array in the List object contains two objects:

        [0] - node label or arc label
        [1] - weight of the defined node/arc

        List<String[] object containing the parsed input graph data
